title: The Nerdist S02E03 - Tribute to Science
description:
Season 2 episode 3 of The Nerdist tv show (originally circulated as season 1 episode 6) 

Airdate: 04/Aug/12 

Host Chris Hardwick, cohosts Matt Mira and Jonah Ray talks science with among other Neil DeGrasse Tyson and Bill Nye.
